'''BMW錦標賽'''（BMW Championship）是美國高爾夫[[PGA巡迴賽|PGA巡迴賽]]的賽事之一，也是聯邦快遞杯四個季后賽賽事中的第三個賽事。BMW錦標賽的前身是西部公開賽（Western Open） <ref>{{cite press release |url=https://www.press.bmwgroup.com/usa/pressDetail.html?title=2013-bmw-championship-earns-pga-tour%25E2%2580%2599s-tournament-of-the-year-honor&outputChannelId=9&id=T0160644EN_US&left_menu_item=node__5122 |title=2013 BMW Championship Earns PGA Tour's Tournament of the Year Honor |publisher=BMW Group |date=October 12, 2013 |access-date=2016-02-22 |archive-date=2014-12-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141209120818/https://www.press.bmwgroup.com/usa/pressDetail.html?title=2013-bmw-championship-earns-pga-tour%25E2%2580%2599s-tournament-of-the-year-honor&outputChannelId=9&id=T0160644EN_US&left_menu_item=node__5122 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。
